c9d7069fffc59939d" class="promo-img" title="Koronavírus a Slovensko" alt="" data-reactid="317"/></a></article></div></div></div><!-- react-empty: 318 --></header></div><div data-reactid="319"><!-- react-empty: 320 --><nav class="container submenu" data-reactid="321"><ul class="submenu-menu menu menu--tabs list-reset clearfix" data-reactid="322"><li class="" data-reactid="323"><a href="/regiony/" data-reactid="324">Všetky</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="325"><a href="/bratislava" data-reactid="326">Hlavné mesto</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="327"><a href="/banskobystricky-kraj" data-reactid="328">Banskobystrický</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="329"><a href="/bratislavsky-kraj" data-reactid="330">Bratislavský</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="331"><a href="/kosicky-kraj" data-reactid="332">Košický</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="333"><a href="/nitriansky-kraj" data-reactid="334">Nitriansky</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="335"><a href="/presovsky-kraj" data-reactid="336">Prešovský</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="337"><a href="/trenciansky-kraj" data-reactid="338">Trenčiansky</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="339"><a href="/trnavsky-kraj" data-reactid="340">Trnavský</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="341"><a href="/zilinsky-kraj" data-reactid="342">Žilinský</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="343"><a href="https://www.teraz.sk/tag/leto2020" rel="noopener" target="_blank" data-reactid="344">Leto na Slovensku</a></li></ul></nav><main data-reactid="345"><article class="article" data-reactid="346"><header class="articleHeader" data-reactid="347"><div class="container" data-reactid="348"><span class="container" data-reactid="349"><a href="/regiony" data-reactid="350"><!-- react-text: 351 -->&lt; sekcia <!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 352 -->Regióny<!-- /react-text --></a></span><h1 class="articleTitle" data-reactid="353">Bratislavský kraj podporuje dohodu medzi hoteliermi a potravinármi</h1><div class="articleActions" data-reactid="354"><div class="articleActions-block" data-reactid="355"><iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/share_button.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teraz.sk%2Fregiony%2Fbsk-kraj-podporuje-dohodu-medzi-hotelie%2F454146-clanok.html&amp;layout=button_count&amp;size=large&amp;mobile_iframe=false&amp;appId=282867128448169&amp;width=110&amp;height=32" width="110" height="32" style="border:none;overflow:hidden;" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" data-reactid="356"></iframe><a class="socialWidget socialWidget--twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teraz.sk%2Fregiony%2Fbsk-kraj-podporuje-dohodu-medzi-hotelie%2F454146-clanok.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-reactid="357"><span class="socialWidget-label" data-reactid="358"><svg class="icon" data-reactid="359"><use xlink:href="/sprite.svg#twitter" data-reactid="360"></use></svg></span></a><a class="socialWidget socialWidget--comments" href="#diskusia" data-reactid="361"><span class="socialWidget-label" data-reactid="362"><svg class="icon" data-reactid="363"><use xlink:href="/sprite.svg#comments" data-reactid="364"></use></svg></span><span class="socialWidget-value" data-reactid="365"><div data-reactid="366"><span class="fb-comments-count" data-href="https://www.teraz.sk/regiony/bsk-kraj-podporuje-dohodu-medzi-hotelie/454146-clanok.html" data-reactid="367">.</span></div></span></a></div></div></div></header><div class="container" data-reactid="368"><div class="l-columns l-columns--article clearfix" data-reactid="369"><div class="articleContent l-main pull-left" data-reactid="370"><div class="articleImage aspectRatio" data-reactid="371"><img src="https://www1.teraz.sk/usercontent/photos/1/c/a/4-1caf8a9a9f86efb07714c7da90ebae3c01814481.jpg" title="Bratislavský kraj podporuje dohodu medzi hoteliermi a potravinármi" alt="" data-reactid="372"/><div class="articleImageTop-caption" data-reactid="373"><figcaption data-reactid="374"><span>Ilustračná foto.</span> <em>Foto: TASR/AP</em><div class="clear"></div></figcaption></div></div><p class="articlePerex" data-reactid="375">Poľnohospodári a potravinári v spolupráci s hoteliermi sa dohodli na výmene informácií o počte pracovníkov, ktorých majú hotelieri a majitelia reštaurácií k dispozícii.</p><div class="articleMeta" data-reactid="376"><div class="clearfix" data-reactid="377"><span class="articleMeta-person" data-reactid="378"><!-- react-text: 379 -->Autor<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 380 --> <!-- /react-text --><strong data-reactid="381"><a href="/author/11" data-reactid="382">TASR</a></strong></span></div><span class="publishingTime" data-reactid="383"><time datetime="2020-03-20T14:45:00+01:00" data-reactid="384">20. marca 2020 14:45</time></span></div><div data-reactid="385"><div id="18abde9b-ad59-4266-a80c-4fdd46fde76d" class="articleMain" data-reactid="386"><div>Bratislava 20. marca (TASR) &ndash; Bratislavsk&yacute; samospr&aacute;vny kraj sa prip&aacute;ja k dohode o vz&aacute;jomnej spolupr&aacute;ci medzi Potravin&aacute;rskou komorou Slovenska (PKS) a Asoci&aacute;ciou hotelov a re&scaron;taur&aacute;ci&iacute; Slovenska (AHRS). Iniciat&iacute;va reaguje na probl&eacute;my, ktor&eacute; vyvstali v s&uacute;vislosti s so &scaron;&iacute;ren&iacute;m nov&eacute;ho koronav&iacute;rusu, sp&ocirc;sobuj&uacute;ceho ochorenie COVID-19.<br>
<br>
Po&#318;nohospod&aacute;ri a potravin&aacute;ri v&nbsp;spolupr&aacute;ci s hoteliermi sa dohodli na v&yacute;mene inform&aacute;ci&iacute; o po&#269;te pracovn&iacute;kov, ktor&yacute;ch maj&uacute; hotelieri a majitelia re&scaron;taur&aacute;ci&iacute; k dispoz&iacute;cii a&nbsp;m&ocirc;&#382;u bez komplik&aacute;ci&iacute; pom&ocirc;c&#357; v&nbsp;potravin&aacute;rskych podnikoch, ke&#271;&#382;e s&uacute; dr&#382;ite&#318;mi zdravotn&yacute;ch preukazov, ktor&eacute; s&uacute; pre pr&aacute;cu v potravin&aacute;rskej v&yacute;robe nevyhnutn&eacute;.<br>
<br>
Aj pod&#318;a predsedu Bratislavsk&eacute;ho samospr&aacute;vneho kraja Juraja Drobu ide o&nbsp;sp&ocirc;sob, ako mo&#382;no pom&ocirc;c&#357; tis&iacute;ckam &#318;ud&iacute;, ktor&iacute; v&nbsp;s&uacute;&#269;asnosti zostali bez pr&aacute;ce a&nbsp;z&aacute;rove&#328; rie&scaron;i&#357; probl&eacute;m v&nbsp;potravin&aacute;rskych podnikoch, poci&#357;uj&uacute;cich zv&yacute;&scaron;en&yacute; dopyt zo strany obchodnej siete, na ktor&eacute;ho uspokojenie v&scaron;ak nemaj&uacute; dostatok pracovnej sily.<br>
<br>
Predseda BSK pripomenul, &#382;e Bratislavsk&eacute;mu kraju, mest&aacute;m a obciam na jeho &uacute;zem&iacute; prin&aacute;&scaron;a turizmus v&yacute;znamn&yacute; ekonomick&yacute; profit. V roku 2019 zaznamenal Bratislavsk&yacute; kraj takmer 1,6 mili&oacute;na n&aacute;v&scaron;tevn&iacute;kov, z dane z ubytovania i zabratia verejn&eacute;ho priestoru maj&uacute; samospr&aacute;vy nemal&yacute; pr&iacute;jem. <i>"H&#318;ad&aacute;me preto sp&ocirc;soby, ako mu pom&ocirc;c&#357;,"</i> doplnil.<br>
<br>
Droba z&aacute;rove&#328; pouk&aacute;zal na to, &#382;e pomocn&uacute; ruku m&ocirc;&#382;u poda&#357; akt&iacute;vne aj samotn&iacute; spotrebitelia.<i> "&#268;oskoro si budeme op&auml;&#357; vybera&#357; dovolenku, pre&#382;ime ju na Slovensku, v slovenskom hoteli. U&#382; teraz m&ocirc;&#382;eme kupova&#357; dom&aacute;ce potraviny a ostatn&eacute; dom&aacute;ce v&yacute;robky, rovnako si m&ocirc;&#382;eme z&nbsp;ob&#318;&uacute;benej re&scaron;taur&aacute;cie objedna&#357; jedlo," </i>uviedol pr&iacute;klad. "Spolo&#269;ne si m&ocirc;&#382;eme takto pom&ocirc;c&#357;, len vz&aacute;jomne sa n&aacute;m &#357;a&#382;k&eacute; &#269;asy podar&iacute; prekona&#357;," zd&ocirc;raznil &scaron;&eacute;f BSK.<br>
<br>
K iniciat&iacute;ve medzi Potravin&aacute;rskou komorou Slovenska a Asoci&aacute;ciou hotelov a re&scaron;taur&aacute;ci&iacute; Slovenska sa zapojili aj &#271;al&scaron;ie organiz&aacute;cie, ako je Zv&auml;z spracovate&#318;ov m&auml;sa, Slovensk&aacute; po&#318;nohospod&aacute;rska a potravin&aacute;rska komora, Slovensk&yacute; mliekarensk&yacute; zv&auml;z, Slovensk&yacute; zv&auml;z pek&aacute;rov, cukr&aacute;rov a cestovin&aacute;rov, &Uacute;nia potravin&aacute;rov Slovenska a ich &#269;lensk&eacute; organiz&aacute;cie.</div>
